<br>
Have a druid harmony him while you move people in place.  Line up melees on left wall in his room, put nuke casters on left side of entrance doorway.  Your main tank (56+ warrior with ripo disc &amp; chain runed) charges it and engages ripo disc, turning to expose it's back to the others, then calls assist and all the other melees charge and the casters nuke.  All melees should use their best fast damage discipline (duelist, mightystrike, fellstrike, etc) except the MT (using ripo disc).<br>
<br>
If you have a strong raid can be done with 12ish (probably even less now with all the SoV, SoL gear that's making the game a joke) <p><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=18807" target="CRProfile" alt="Yunna's Profile" title="Yunna's Profile"><img src="http://24.101.174.177/scripts/rsig/yunnasig.php" border="0" alt=""></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uulaian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ulaian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Whore</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/17/02 1:57:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumwizard.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=255.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: VS Tactics</span><hr size=1> If you think you can kill him in 20secs if he doesnt get any lifetaps in, you might consider having a ranger tank him with Weaponshield. <p>Ulaian Moonleaf <BR>
